{"title_page": "V\u0103c\u0103reni", "text_new": "{{Infobox Romanian subdivision\n|type                   = commune\n|county                 = Tulcea\n|population_total       = auto\n|map_caption            = Location in Tulcea County\n| name                    = V\u0103c\u0103reni\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_caption           = \n| image_shield            = \n|image_map              = Vacareni jud Tulcea.png\n| coordinates             = {{coord|45|19|N|28|12|E|type:city|display=inline,title}}\n| established_date        = \n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_total_km2          = \n| leader_party            = \n| leader_title            = <!-- Mayor -->\n| leader_name             = \n| postal_code             =\n| website                 = \n| footnotes               = \n}}\n'''V\u0103c\u0103reni''' is a commune in [[Tulcea County]], [[Romania]]. It is composed of a single village, V\u0103c\u0103reni. This belonged to [[Luncavi\u021ba, Tulcea|Luncavi\u021ba]] Commune until 2003, when it was split off.\n\nSouthwest of V\u0103c\u0103reni, there is a 218 metres tall guyed mast for FM-/TV-broadcasting and a [[V\u0103c\u0103reni Wind Farm|wind farm]] is planned.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n*{{GEOnet|-1173460}}\n\n{{Tulcea County}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vacareni}}\n[[Category:Communes in Tulcea County]]\n\n{{Tulcea-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Romanian subdivision\n|type                   = commune\n|county                 = Tulcea\n|population_total       = auto\n|map_caption            = Location in Tulcea County\n| name                    = V\u0103c\u0103reni\n| image_skyline           = \n| imagesize               = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| image_shield            = \n| shield_alt              = \n| image_map               = \n| coordinates             = {{coord|45|19|N|28|12|E|type:city|display=inline,title}}\n| established_date        = \n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_total_km2          = \n| leader_party            = \n| leader_title            = <!-- Mayor -->\n| leader_name             = \n| postal_code             =\n| website                 = \n| footnotes               = \n}}\n'''V\u0103c\u0103reni''' is a commune in [[Tulcea County]], [[Romania]]. It is composed of a single village, V\u0103c\u0103reni. This belonged to [[Luncavi\u021ba, Tulcea|Luncavi\u021ba]] Commune until 2003, when it was split off.\n\nSouthwest of V\u0103c\u0103reni, there is a 218 metres tall guyed mast for FM-/TV-broadcasting and a [[V\u0103c\u0103reni Wind Farm|wind farm]] is planned.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n*{{GEOnet|-1173460}}\n\n{{Tulcea County}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vacareni}}\n[[Category:Communes in Tulcea County]]\n\n{{Tulcea-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Markussep", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/V%C4%83c%C4%83reni"}
{"title_page": "Ogden, Utah", "text_new": "{{short description|City in Utah, United States}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See Template:Infobox Settlement for additional fields that may be available-->\n<!--See the Table at Infobox Settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->| currency = dollar($)\n| official_name                   = Ogden, Utah\n| native_name                     = <!-- for cities whose native name is not in English -->\n| nickname                        = Junction City\n| settlement_type                 = [[City]]\n| motto                           = Still Untamed\n<!-- images and maps  ----------->\n| image_skyline                   = US Utah Ogden Montage.jpg\n| imagesize                       = \n| image_caption                   = From top left to bottom right: Ogden High School, Weber State University Bell Tower, Peery's Egyptian Theater, Downtown, Gantry Sign, aerial view\n| image_flag                      = \n| flag_size                       = \n| image_seal                      = \n| seal_size                       = \n| image_shield                    = \n| shield_size                     = \n| image_blank_emblem              = \n| blank_emblem_type               = \n| blank_emblem_size               = \n| image_map                       = Weber County Utah incorporated and unincorporated areas Ogden highlighted.svg\n| mapsize                         = 260px\n| map_caption                     = Location in [[Weber County, UT|Weber County]] and the state of [[Utah]]\n<!-- Location ------------------>\n| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = [[United States]]\n| subdivision_type1               = [[U.S. state|State]]\n| subdivision_name1               = [[Utah]]\n| subdivision_type2               = [[List of counties in Utah|County]]\n| subdivision_name2               = [[Weber County, Utah|Weber]]\n| subdivision_type3               = \n| subdivision_name3   